<section class = "media-partner-about-container">
  <h2 class = "subhead">About</h2>
  <p class = "media-partner-about-blurb">The Kent Stater is the award-winning, student-run newspaper at Kent State University.
    Reaching more than 15,000 people per issue, the Stater keeps the community up-to-date with campus, local and national news,
    sports and features. The Stater publishes on Monday, Wednesday and Thursday and has a circulation of 6,750 per day.
    During the summer months, The Kent Stater runs special print issues and also runs the annual Orientation issue to
    welcome new and returning students.</p>

